case "${ACTION}" in
post)
	cat <<_EOF
==========================================================================

To use KVM your user must be added to the 'wheel' group:

	$ usermod -aG wheel <username>

Don't forget to load the appropiate KVM module for your CPU:

	$ modprobe kvm-amd # for AMD CPUs
	$ modprobe kvm-intel # for Intel CPUs

==========================================================================
_EOF
	;;
esac
